title: Krak Session – Cladel Skatepark
content:
Here is another episode of our “Krak session”, this time at the parisian street-skatepark of Cladel.

Pass by if you ever around, the park is fun and the locals are cool!

Join the club to see what is happening skate-wise in your city and join our sessions!
